data.description: Check out this quaint, super cute, well-maintained & updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with carport! This home in Talladega has a large shaded yard and is located in town. Newly renovated with energy efficient heating and air. 22 SER cooling and 9.80 HSPF. New bathroom and kitchen fixtures, new flooring, fresh paint. Both kitchen and bathrooms have been updated. Large walk-in pantry with built in shelving directly off the kitchen. Kitchen window facing oversized backyard where you can enjoy the large lot. Ceiling fans in living room and 2 bedrooms. Separate laundry/utility room with large walk-in closet for storage. Spacious half basement. This home is move-in ready and waiting on you!
